  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/5915a3e16a6563e28c1ffb6429fae1f4.avif?t=1715515678\" width=460 height=214 /></span><br><strong>Living Dead is a fun coop wave based 3D shooter from a top view perspective. The Game takes place in a simulation of a zombie shooter and the goal is to survive as much waves as possible or beat them all. Each wave becomes more difficult than the previous one. By killing zombies you can acquire new weapons that will help you survive the swarm of zombies.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 player co-op or solo play<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/e1799e220864d5d8ccae6cf886d8c0e3.poster.avif?t=1715515678\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/e1799e220864d5d8ccae6cf886d8c0e3.webm?t=1715515678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/e1799e220864d5d8ccae6cf886d8c0e3.mp4?t=1715515678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Earn and unlock unique skins (10 per class)<br></li><li>Huge variety of guns (currently over 50)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/fda057854cf8f4062309ceb51f65538c.poster.avif?t=1715515678\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/fda057854cf8f4062309ceb51f65538c.webm?t=1715515678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/fda057854cf8f4062309ceb51f65538c.mp4?t=1715515678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Class progression system<br></li><li>Survive hordes of zombies alone or with friends</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/5915a3e16a6563e28c1ffb6429fae1f4.avif?t=1715515678\" width=460 height=214 /></span><br><strong>Living Dead is a fun coop wave based 3D shooter from a top view perspective. The Game takes place in a simulation of a zombie shooter and the goal is to survive as much waves as possible or beat them all. Each wave becomes more difficult than the previous one. By killing zombies you can acquire new weapons that will help you survive the swarm of zombies.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 player co-op or solo play<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/e1799e220864d5d8ccae6cf886d8c0e3.poster.avif?t=1715515678\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/e1799e220864d5d8ccae6cf886d8c0e3.webm?t=1715515678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/e1799e220864d5d8ccae6cf886d8c0e3.mp4?t=1715515678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Earn and unlock unique skins (10 per class)<br></li><li>Huge variety of guns (currently over 50)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/fda057854cf8f4062309ceb51f65538c.poster.avif?t=1715515678\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/fda057854cf8f4062309ceb51f65538c.webm?t=1715515678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084840/extras/fda057854cf8f406230